CustomField.description: For sync time log records, it is the time taken by the client app to process sync response, with the value calculated using this formula: Client Response Processing Timestamp - Client Response Receive Timestamp. It is in seconds if Type is MASTER_*; milliseconds otherwise.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: For sync time log records, it is the time taken by the client app to process sync response: Client Response Processing Timestamp - Client Response Receive Timestamp. It is in seconds if Type is MASTER_*; milliseconds otherwise.
CustomField.label: Log Context
